Class NodeImpl<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
      • java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
        • java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
          • dht.NodeImpl<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - is the type of value that is stored in the table.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DHT<E>, Node<E>, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote

    public class NodeImpl<E>
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements Node<E>, DHT<E>
    The implementation of a node/peer in the distributed hash table. Interfaces for usage and node-to-node communication are implemented.
    Author:
    Andreas
